# POOL-INIT.gal

## Purpose
Describes the initialization and bootstrap process for a new Galaxy Node Pool instance.

## Steps
1. Configure `example.yaml` with pool/server settings
2. Build and run the pool engine (Go binary or Docker)
3. Register plugins via config
4. Start accepting node registrations and heartbeats
5. Monitor logs and metrics

## Notes
- Reference POOL-CONFIG.gal for all settings
- Reference POOL-PLUGINS.gal for available plugins

